cs.CR, cs.DC, cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.DS 

The paper discusses security and privacy issues in cloud computing, which is a major concern in the field of computer security (cs.CR). It also talks about the architecture and infrastructure of cloud computing (cs.DC), and the need for addressing issues related to interoperability (cs.SE) and community of interest (cs.CY). The paper also mentions the possibility of denial of service attacks (cs.DS) and the use of mobile cloud computing (MCC) and optical character recognition (OCR) technologies.
